modelVersions.name: Shurik-V1
modelVersions.description:
Examples use Realistic Vision V1.3, The Ally's Mix III: Revolutions and AbyssOrangeMix2 - SFW.

Play with weights. My examples use 0.9

Others have made Jennifer Connelly stuff, but I haven't.

Dataset included her as a young adult, her more recent older self and everything in between. I was hoping it would capture the best of both worlds if I trained it all together.
